entries.journal_entry_description: Boba Fett has employed you. It's usually a good idea to do what he suggests. People that don't play their cards right against Fett has a habit of catching a case of death.
entries.journal_entry_title: Working for Boba Fett, phase II
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: The bartender in the labor outpost on Yavin 4 said that Wogo was going to Nashal on Talus. Cantina's have worked so far, check if he's at the Nashal one.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Apparently Uff Wogo is in the back room of the cantina. Time to finish the job.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: The bounty hunter Durge has already killed Wogo. He's allowed you to take the gun out of the box he stuffed him in, if you deliver a message to Fett.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You should return to Boba Fett with the gun and explain to him what happened.
